{
  "stem": "5328.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whatever was left over from the carrot from the rabbits, I ate it up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- and then-- because-- after-- right after there were so many screaming, yelling, and taking out people from the hiding spaces and putting on the-- on the trucks and kill-- kills them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it quiet down-- after two days, it quiet done already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You didn't hear the screaming and the-- from the people from-- so I wanted to go out from that place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't open the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like I said, I was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was skinny and small, and I couldn't open that door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She-- They-- they closed the door from the outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The door of the barn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I found out that there's another young man was in-- hidden too and just the two of us left-- left in that barn.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So middle of the night, he walked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went down, and he tore up a piece of the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you asked me, said, let's-- let's be together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let's go together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Wherever we'll go, we'll go together, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said-- but first, you go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He told me, you go out and look around, if there's safe to-- to be out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if it's safe, come back, and we'll go together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I looked around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I was afraid to go back and call on him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was-- every time we-- I looked, I thought everybody knows that I'm Jewish, a Jewish child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they'll kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went without him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And up to date, I still have a guilty conscience why I didn't go and pick him up too-- the way we talked.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
